  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to assess different methods for early adiposity rebound determination at the
      age of 4/5 years old according to current medical screening criteria in schools, and to
      assess their prognostic value for obesity amongst 11 years old pre-adolescents according to
      the known risk factors.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
